  "riddle": "1. Unearth the tale of a tech giant born in 1975 — what year marked the beginning of this innovative venture?\n\n2. Now that you have a significant number, what is the next prime that follows it on the numerical road?\n\n3. Seek the narrative of a company that evolved through code and creativity; from what date did it truly come to life?\n\n4. If you wish to grasp the vast timeline of acquisitions, calculate the total days from April 4, 1975, to March 17, 2026. \n\n5. Track down the digital playground named after a console — when did the network first open its gates to players?\n\n6. A fresh quest lies ahead; find the year in which an organization devoted to artificial intelligence found its footing.\n\n7. The journey continues: what is the sum of the distinct prime factors of the year you just acquired? \n\n8. A tech hub bustling with innovation, located on the West Coast, awaits. What coordinates mark the heart of this vibrant city?\n\n9. A question of elevation rises next: how high does the ground sit beneath the buildings in this urban landscape?\n\n10. Nearby, knowledge abounds; how many libraries can you find nestled in this city of tech?\n\n11. Combine the elevation from clue 9 with the library count from clue 10: find the absolute difference between them.\n\n12. Another city, filled with cultural vibrancy, beckons. How many languages does its own Wikipedia page cater to?\n\n13. To traverse to this city, determine how high above sea level it stands.\n\n14. A similar inquiry unfolds: what is the count of libraries available in this educational hub?\n\n15. Merge the information — add the elevation you found in clue 13 to the library count from clue 14.\n\n16. Count up the stadiums in this tech-savvy region. What number do you discover nearby?\n\n17. At last, blend the insights from clues 1 and 2: compute the absolute difference between clue 1 and clue 2, and take that result modulo 10. Your response should be a single digit between 0 and 9.",
